<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:26:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57def86f2c7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;抱歉，我们已经打烊了。营业中，请进。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="White storefront on a street corner with white iron bars on all of the windows and the front door. Everything is weathered. There is one sign in the window that reads “sorry, we’re closed,” and a second in an adjacent window that reads “open, come in.” There are wig busts in the window with various head wraps on them. A sign painted on the concrete at the entryway reads “national shirt shops coast to coast.”" height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a57def86f2c7.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:26:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57ddbbe4596</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于图森市中心的芝加哥音乐商店。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Front of a music store in an old brick and concrete building, painted dark red. The sign on the building reads “new and used pianos and organs,” with a decorative letter “c” at the edge where store’s name begins. There are many stacked drum sets in the windows with many sale signs." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a57ddbbe4596.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:21:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57d2c420fea</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被囚禁的&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A close-up black and white photograph captures a toucan with its large, distinctive beak." height="1600" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/cliff538/6a57d2c420fea.jpg" width="2400"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://cliff538.some.pics"&gt;@cliff538&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:34:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57d259e2374</link><description>&lt;p&gt;羽毛维护&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A colorful blue and yellow macaw is perched on a branch, preening its feathers against a blurred green background." height="1600" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/cliff538/6a57d259e2374.jpg" width="2400"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://cliff538.some.pics"&gt;@cliff538&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:33:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Crown of Light</title><link>https://some.pics/6a57d214c6afc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;光之冠&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A peacock displays its long, vibrant tail feathers with eye-like patterns while perched on a fence under sunlight filtering through the trees." height="2400" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/cliff538/6a57d214c6afc.jpg" width="1364"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://cliff538.some.pics"&gt;@cliff538&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:31:53 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>